OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773667692
OL,3,CGuernsey firm fined almost #2 million
OL,4,Cfor underestimating financial crime
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FA Guernsey company has been fined
OL,8,Fnearly #2 million for underestimating
OL,9,Fthe degree of financial crime risk
OL,10,Frelated to it life insurance business.
OL,12,FThe Guernsey Financial Services
OL,13,FCommission (GFSC) have fined Utmost
OL,14,FWorld Wide Limited #1,960,000, the
OL,15,Flargest fine its ever issued, for
OL,16,Fbreaches of regulation spanning a ten
OL,17,Fyear period.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773667692
OL,3,CGuernsey firm fined almost #2 million
OL,4,Cfor underestimating financial crime
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FTwo employees Leon Steyn, the Chief
OL,8,FFinancial Officer and James Alexander
OL,9,FWatchorn the Nominated Officer /
OL,10,FDeputy Money Laundering Reporting
OL,11,FOfficer were also fined for their role
OL,12,Fin breaking the regulations.
OL,14,FThe fines relate to serious and
OL,15,Fsystemic failings between 2015 and
OL,16,F2025.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773667692
OL,3,CGuernsey firm fined almost #2 million
OL,4,Cfor underestimating financial crime
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FThe Guernsey Financial Services
OL,8,FCommission found the risk of financial
OL,9,Fcrime was increased by the company's
OL,10,Fhistoric business model, which related
OL,11,Fto using brokers that were unregulated
OL,12,Ffor international business, and who
OL,13,Fwere operating in developing countries
OL,14,Fwith weak financial crime
OL,15,Finfrastructure.
OL,17,FIt also had clients that were both
OL,18,Flocal and international executives and
OL,19,Fbusiness stretching back decades when
OL,20,Ffinancial crime requirements were less
OL,21,Frigorous.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773667692
OL,3,CGuernsey firm fined almost #2 million
OL,4,Cfor underestimating financial crime
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FThe GFSC said the Utmost World Wide
OL,8,FLimited assessed its business as low
OL,9,Frisk, despite many of its clients
OL,10,Fbeing high risk and it made little
OL,11,Feffort to monitor clients until they
OL,12,Fhad to pay out.
OL,14,FThe firm had at one point
OL,15,Fapproximately 22,500 high-risk
OL,16,Fclients, but based on its processes
OL,17,Fwould review less than 3.5% of those
OL,18,Fon an annual basis.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773667692
OL,3,CGuernsey firm fined almost #2 million
OL,4,Cfor underestimating financial crime
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FThe very small number of high-risk
OL,8,Fclients that were subject to regular
OL,9,Freview, represented the company's
OL,10,Fhighest risk clients, including
OL,11,FPolitically Exposed Persons.
OL,13,FThe GFSC also found that these reviews
OL,14,Fwere also ineffective due to the lack
OL,15,Fof customer contact, and the fact that
OL,16,Fcustomer due diligence problems found
OL,17,Fduring these reviews were not always
OL,18,Faddressed at the time, but deferred
OL,19,Funtil a future review.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773667692
OL,3,CGuernsey firm fined almost #2 million
OL,4,Cfor underestimating financial crime
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FThe commission said in their report:
OL,8,F"The Licensee was therefore unable to
OL,9,Fdemonstrate a meaningful and up-to-
OL,10,Fdate understanding of the financial
OL,11,Fcrime risks of its clients, in
OL,12,Fparticular, its high-risk clients.
OL,14,F"This led to widespread failings and
OL,15,Fsystemic breaches of the regulatory
OL,16,Frequirements of the Bailiwick in
OL,17,Frelation to risk assessments,
OL,18,Fmonitoring, and the source of wealth
OL,19,Fand source of funds of its high-risk
OL,20,Fclient base."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773667692
OL,3,CGuernsey firm fined almost #2 million
OL,4,Cfor underestimating financial crime
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FA GFSC spokesperson said in a
OL,8,Fstatement there is no evidence of
OL,9,Fcriminal investigation at this stage.
OL,11,FIt added: "We have regular meetings
OL,12,Fseveral times a year with the Economic
OL,13,Fand Financial Crime Bureau to share
OL,14,Finformation on matters of common
OL,15,Finterest, particularly ongoing
OL,16,Finvestigations and information which
OL,17,Fwe both may acquire about possible law
OL,18,Fbreaking. It is not our place to talk
OL,19,Fabout any criminal investigations on
OL,20,Fany matter."
OL,26,@sD@KOU|D@LO]
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773667692
OL,3,CGuernsey firm fined almost #2 million
OL,4,Cfor underestimating financial crime
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FLeon Steyn was fined #35,000 for his
OL,8,Frole in the regulation breaches. He
OL,9,Fwas Chief Financial Officer of the
OL,10,Ffirm from September 2012 to April
OL,11,F2020, a Director from 28 February
OL,12,F2019, and the Chief Executive Officer
OL,13,Ffrom 21 April 2020 to date.
OL,15,FThe Commission investigation found
OL,16,Fthat Mr Steyn failed to consistently
OL,17,Fact with competence, soundness of
OL,18,Fjudgement and diligence (for his part
OL,19,Fas CEO) by:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773667692
OL,3,CGuernsey firm fined almost #2 million
OL,4,Cfor underestimating financial crime
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FJames Watchorn was fined #10,500. He
OL,8,Fwas the Nominated Officer / Deputy
OL,9,FMoney Laundering Reporting Officer
OL,10,Ffrom 16 August 2018 until 2025.
OL,12,FThe GFSC investigation found that Mr
OL,13,FWatchorn failed to consistently act
OL,14,Fwith competence, soundness of
OL,15,Fjudgement and diligence by:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773667692
OL,3,CGuernsey firm fined almost #2 million
OL,4,Cfor underestimating financial crime
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FThe Guernsey Financial Services
OL,8,FCommission said in 2023 Mr Steyn did
OL,9,Fstart a remediation programme which
OL,10,Fincluded new risk assessment methods
OL,11,Fand he significantly changed the way
OL,12,Fthe company reviewed it client risk
OL,13,Fassessments.
OL,15,FThe company also re-rated all its
OL,16,Fclients and will review them more
OL,17,Fregularly. But the GFSC said the level
OL,18,Fof change needed to bring it up to
OL,19,Fstandard will take some time.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
