PN,38611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773667692
OL,3,CGuernsey firm fined almost #2 million
OL,4,Cfor underestimating financial crime
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FIt also stated that Mr Steyn and Mr
OL,8,FWatchhorn both assisted the Commission
OL,9,Ffully during the investigation.
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/11
